data.description:
**UPDATE**

Tatiana has been located and is safe. Thank you.
____________

Deputies with the Greenville County Sheriff's Office are seeking information regarding the whereabouts of a runaway teenager. Last night (February 9, 2021), at around 11:00pm, Tatiana Ortiz ran away from a residence on Boswell Court and has not been seen since.

We ask for anyone who sees her or has information regarding her whereabouts to call 864-271-5210 or Crime Stoppers of Greenville at 23-CRIME.
